HEADWORD: Honewort
<hw>Hone"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An umbelliferous plant of the genus <gen>Sison</gen> (<spn>Sison
Amomum</spn>); -- so called because used to cure a swelling called a
<xex>hone</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

